cd69599b-07d3-4241-9371-65d954a5e4e5.title: Norman
cd69599b-07d3-4241-9371-65d954a5e4e5.text: Quickly, tell me - is it still there?

18f05b8a-4e89-478b-8585-dffe6252913b.title: Norman
18f05b8a-4e89-478b-8585-dffe6252913b.text:
The THING, the THING! It was just outside my
house! Has it gone away yet? Or is it still lurking out
there, waiting for me to go outside?

cd238677-67c7-4a82-9d94-1f4ef148b779.title: <player>
cd238677-67c7-4a82-9d94-1f4ef148b779.text:
I didn't see any THING out there, just a couple of
guards. What did it look like?

9b0c341d-5efa-4d0c-bf21-6956a61e854f.title: Norman
9b0c341d-5efa-4d0c-bf21-6956a61e854f.text:
Ohhhh, it was HORRIBLE! It was an enormous
THING, with TEETH and EYES and... and... and
THINGS!

03331deb-0794-4ce2-9c91-89546e57bffa.title: <player>
03331deb-0794-4ce2-9c91-89546e57bffa.text: Um... would you care to be more specific?

67f40c22-9585-4d0d-a99d-a24d79fda70c.title: Norman
67f40c22-9585-4d0d-a99d-a24d79fda70c.text: I can't. I only saw it in the dark.

ed0a46f3-c418-48e3-99e6-bcbd18210752.title: <player>
ed0a46f3-c418-48e3-99e6-bcbd18210752.text: You only saw this THING in the dark?

068c8f05-339b-4bff-8ecb-d363d287f9e4.title: Norman
068c8f05-339b-4bff-8ecb-d363d287f9e4.text:
I was sleeping peacefully one night, when suddenly I
woke up and saw it through the window. It was
LOOKING at me! I haven't dared go out since then.
It's had me trapped in here for days! I've packed my

1610f1a2-5d76-4d15-b6e8-894d8de82af0.title: Norman
1610f1a2-5d76-4d15-b6e8-894d8de82af0.text:
bags so I can escape, but the THING's still out there
waiting for me to come out! If I have to stay in here
much longer I'll go mad! MAD!! MAD!!!

b98dca3d-4ed9-470d-8e35-a2aafd6ae83a.title: <player>
b98dca3d-4ed9-470d-8e35-a2aafd6ae83a.text:
There's no THING outside. Just come out and get
some fresh air before you go funny in the head.

5ba1e55a-df34-43d7-9005-d7d40845378b.title: Norman
5ba1e55a-df34-43d7-9005-d7d40845378b.text: You want me to go outside?

ca55a849-7c4a-4c8c-bbbc-e3d3f92feac4.title: <player>
ca55a849-7c4a-4c8c-bbbc-e3d3f92feac4.text:
I think you might just have dreamed about the
THING.

04782e65-7b1b-4f95-8be4-1f9023904f1a.title: Norman
04782e65-7b1b-4f95-8be4-1f9023904f1a.text: You want me to believe that it's not real?

2c87c6c3-1609-43ea-8c39-4442f323d6f5.title: Norman
2c87c6c3-1609-43ea-8c39-4442f323d6f5.text:
No! No! I know what you are! You're in league with
the THING! It keeps sending people in here to trick
me into going outside! They keep stealing from me too!
GO AWAY!

0fd099ee-be73-4bf6-b851-21805182c4d1.title: <player>
0fd099ee-be73-4bf6-b851-21805182c4d1.text: I'm not trying to trick you!
